The paper deals with the formal language theory and parsing algorithms, which are typically covered in the sub-categories of Formal Languages and Automata Theory (cs.FL), Programming Languages (cs.PL), and Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS). The paper also discusses the Boolean closure and hierarchy of languages, which are related to Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO) and Computational Complexity (cs.CC).
